{%- comment -%}

  HOW TO USE

  To create a new, unique Content Landing Page:
    - Create Page in the Admin
    - set Template to page.content-landing
    - go to More Actions -> Add Metafields to page
    - in the 'content_landing_key' metafield, enter a unique value (ex. 'abc123')
    - copy all contents from sections/content-landing.liquid and paste into a new file
    - name the new file 'content-landing_<key>' with a single underscore + key (ex. 'content-landing_abc123.liquid')
    - in this file, add a case block that matches the key and use the new section 

{%- endcomment -%}

{% liquid 
  assign key = page.metafields.global.content_landing_key | handleize

  case key

    when 'mens'
      section 'kit-landing-mens'

    when 'womens'
      section 'kit-landing-womens'

    when 'kids'
      section 'kit-landing-kids'

    else
      section 'content-landing'

  endcase
%}